After merging with default I saw that a couple of tests were failing due to pull request #1954. We probably missed them before because they were not running on Jenkins.

I fixed the tests and added a couple of other lines to the tests in branch [config_tests_louise](#!/osrf/gazebo/commits/f6492ee9eac94fc237eeb7059f9643b281ae61d5), started a [coverage](http://build.osrfoundation.org/view/main/view/CI%20coverage%20jobs/job/gazebo-any-coverage-trusty-amd64/467/) build for that branch. Feel free to merge it in if it's ok.

I fixed the tests and added a couple of other lines to the tests in branch config_tests_louise, started a coverage build for that branch. Feel free to merge it in if it's ok.
